Changes since last version
==========================

ffmpeg_analyze: better detection of correct channels (reads the info from ffmpeg decoder if available)

ebu_r128:	adjusted the windowsize of integrated mode to properly overlap
		added option to change relative gate (expected to switch from 8 to 10dB in the future), see api for more info




